WEBVTT

00:11:28.880 --> 00:11:30.256
And see, that's the problem.

00:11:30.280 --> 00:11:32.136
It's totally cool for men to follow me

00:11:32.160 --> 00:11:35.296
when I talk about guy stuff

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:37.040
and I conform to gender norms.

00:11:38.080 --> 00:11:42.296
But if I talk about
how much I love my wife

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:45.200
or my daughter or my 10-day-old son,

00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:50.736
how I believe that marriage
is challenging but beautiful,

00:11:50.760 --> 00:11:54.016
or how as a man
I struggle with body dysmorphia,

00:11:54.040 --> 00:11:56.920
or if I promote gender equality,
then only the women show up.

00:11:58.200 --> 00:11:59.400
Where are the men?